Package com.satvik.struct

Class LinkedList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.satvik.struct.LinkedList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of Items the LinkeeList contains
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Queue, Stack

    public class LinkedList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class describes a list comprised of ListItems linked together. Items can be pushed and popped into and out of the list.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0, 04/07/2016
    Author:
    Satvik Saha
